  <description><![CDATA[<h2>Explore two of the Tyrol's most-loved walking destinations this multi-centre holiday to Kitzbühel and Mayrhofen</h2>
<p>A multi-centre holiday to <a data-udi="umb://document/0424394c50b54ef4848722ee185d0739" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0424394c50b54ef4848722ee185d0739}" title="Kitzbuhel">Kitzbühel</a> and Mayrhofen means you get to experience some of the best walking trails in the Austrian Tyrol. Spend a couple of days exploring the small, colourful city of Kitzbühel, enjoy spectacular views of the mountains, and make use of the great lift network. Then, visit Mayrhofen and head out into the vast area of the Zillertal, with miles of walking trails, traditional mountain huts and lots of activities to try too.</p>
<h3>Guide price from: £1,450pp* </h3>
<h3>Your multi-centre holiday options: </h3>
<ul>
<li style="list-style-type: none;">
<ul>
<li>Travel and change destination on a Wednesday or Saturday</li>
<li>Combine stays of 3, 4, 7, 10 or 11 nights into a total holiday duration of 7, 10, 11 or 14 nights</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h3>Your holiday includes:</h3>
<ul>
<ul>
<li>Return flights from the UK</li>
<li>Transfers from the airport to your hotel in Kitzbühel, from your hotel in Kitzbühel to your hotel in Mayrhofen and from your hotel in Mayrhofen to the airport</li>
<li>Accommodation in your chosen hotel in each destination</li>
</ul>
</ul>
<p> </p>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-grey c-card--generic-shadow ">
<div class="c-card_content c-section u-margin-top u-margin-bottom u-margin-left u-margin-right">
<h2 style="text-align: center;">How to Book Your Multi-Centre Holiday</h2>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>Simply give us a call to book your multi-centre holiday. Flights, hotel and transport? Consider it done. Dial in and let our experts plan your dream getaway. </span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call Us to Book Today</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p><em>*Prices are based on 2 people sharing for 4 nights in a Standard Room at Hotel Schweizerhof, Kitzbühel and 3 nights in a Austrian Twin Room at Hotel Forsterhaus zum Kramerwirt, Mayrhofen with shared transfers between resorts, departing on the 24th May 25 from Manchester airport. Supplements for alternative flights, flight routes, and room types may apply. Prices are correct at the time of publishing on 9th Dec 24 but are subject to change based on availability. Please call for the most up-to-date pricing and availability before booking.</em></p>]]></description>
