  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<h2>Hotels in Kitzbühel</h2>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/bcd939339a954247961c692e5f66f8b8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bcd939339a954247961c692e5f66f8b8}" title="Hotel Tiefenbrunner">Hotel Tiefenbrunner</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13106106/hotel_tiefenbrunner_kitzbuhel_kneipp_pond.jpg?width=320&amp;height=220" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/8bb047d488d840a98a3ddcfd954e5c7b" /></p>
<p>Ideally located in the centre of Kitzbühel, the Hotel Tiefenbrunner is everything you need for a comfortable and convenient stay, with excellent food and service. There's an indoor pool and spa, perfect for post-hike relaxation and the garden is a suprisingly peaceful oasis, with plenty of space for dozing in the sunshine or shade.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/dcecccebd4fc4260b26e10a4cdbe9071" href="/{localLink:umb://document/dcecccebd4fc4260b26e10a4cdbe9071}" title="Aktivhotel Schweizerhof">Hotel Schweizerhof</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13106105/aktivhotel_schweizerhof_kitzbuhel_exterior.jpg?width=320&amp;height=220" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/692a68c4bca74f6baa23ca3da81ca097" /></p>
<p>Located close to the bottom of the Hahnenkamm lift, it doesn't get much easier to head out into the mountains than at the Hotel Schweizerhof, and at the end of a good day's walking, you'll return to an indoor pool and spa where you can relax before indulging in the excellent half board dinner. On a sunny afternoon, the terrace is a lovely spot for a drink.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/0424394c50b54ef4848722ee185d0739" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0424394c50b54ef4848722ee185d0739}" title="Kitzbuhel" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn c-btn--mid c-btn--secondary-hollow c-btn--wide u-text-center">View all Hotels in Kitzbühel</a></p>
<p><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call Us to Book Today</a></p>]]></facilityDescription>
  <familyDescription><![CDATA[<h2>Hotels in Mayrhofen</h2>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/0e3acebd773c41129a5137bcda17e19c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0e3acebd773c41129a5137bcda17e19c}" title="Alpenhotel Kramerwirt">Alpenhotel Kramerwirt</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13104909/kramerwirt.jpg?width=320&amp;height=220" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/9f19800a81a34016bbdf1745e6b320a8" />Ideally located in the centre of Mayrhofen, the Hotel Kramerwirt is close to the train station and only a short walk to the Penken Lift. Its highlight has to be the rooftop whirlpool and spa which are perfect for a bit of rest and relaxation, and there's great food to refuel on for your next adventure.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/671cb984128c4634a2684280b5239b73" href="/{localLink:umb://document/671cb984128c4634a2684280b5239b73}" title="Elisabeth Hotel">Hotel Elisabeth</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13104910/elisabethhotel-schwimmbad.jpg?width=320&amp;height=220" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/a24f5bb44756480c85d3b7fdfe43b07e" /></p>
<p>Indulge in a bit of luxury at the adults-only Hotel Elisabeth. The excellent spa facilities are extensive, with indoor pool, whirlpool and a variety of saunas and steam rooms to choose from. Stylish rooms, a warm welcome and a high standard of food make this hotel a great choice for a relaxing holiday.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/594483304a5f4b47844b444df2c9d975" href="/{localLink:umb://document/594483304a5f4b47844b444df2c9d975}" title="Mayrhofen" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn c-btn--mid c-btn--secondary-hollow c-btn--wide u-text-center">View all Hotels in Mayrhofen</a></p>
<p><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call Us to Book Today</a></p>]]></familyDescription>
