  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>Explore two of the Tyrol's most popular walking destinations this multi-centre holiday to Kitzbühel and Mayrhofen. Spend your first week exploring the vibrant mountain city of Kitzbühel and the walking trails of the Kitzbüheler Horn and Hahnenkamm. Then, spend a week in Mayrhofen exploring the extensive trail network of the Zillertal, with hiker's lifts and an abundance of activities.</p>]]></listingDescription>
