  <locationDescription><![CDATA[<p>A multi-centre holiday lets you mix and match hotels, lengths of stay, and exciting activities to create your ideal trip. Enjoy everything from panoramic walks, cultural tours and outdoor adventures to relaxing days and tasty local cuisine.</p>
<h3>Visit the colourful city of Kitzbühel and explore the extensive network of walking trails</h3>
<p>Kitzbühel is surrounded by one of the largest hiking trail networks in Austria so there's lots to explore, and panoramic views in all directions. Back in the vibrant centre of the city, there's excellent restaurants, fancy boutiques and cafes that spill out onto the streets. Take the lift up the Hahnenkamm to hike the famous Streif route, or enjoy a paddleboard on the Schwarzsee lake. There's a great network of lifts so getting to the best view points really easy and there's lots of activities to try like e-biking or mountain-biking.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/0424394c50b54ef4848722ee185d0739" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0424394c50b54ef4848722ee185d0739}" title="Kitzbuhel" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn c-btn--mid c-btn--secondary-hollow c-btn--wide u-text-center">Find Out More About Kitzbühel</a></p>
<h3>Explore the vast walking trails and views of the Zillertal from Mayrhofen</h3>
<p>The valleys branching away from Mayrhofen offer a plethora of walking trails to explore and picturesque views are easy to come by. Walk to the famous Berliner Hut with impressive views of the glaciers, or join an Inghams guided walk to get insider info and the best local trails and hidden gems. Take a trip to Krimml Waterfalls, make the most of the excellent lift network to to the best viewpoints or perhaps try some river sports like rafting - there's something for everyone in the Zillertal.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/594483304a5f4b47844b444df2c9d975" href="/{localLink:umb://document/594483304a5f4b47844b444df2c9d975}" title="Mayrhofen" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn c-btn--mid c-btn--secondary-hollow c-btn--wide u-text-center">Find Out More About Mayrhofen</a></p>
<p><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call Us to Book Today</a></p>
<p><em>Please note: This is an independent multi-centre holiday and you are free to choose your own itinerary in each destination. The above contains recommendations which are provided for information only and are not included in the price of your holiday. An Inghams Destination Expert will be on hand locally either in resort or by telephone and will provide advice and offer optional excursions and walking passes.</em></p>
<p><em>Special diets, including vegetarian, must be requested prior to booking.</em></p>
<p><em>The itineraries may be subject to change. Where this becomes necessary, and where practicable, we will take the steps as outlined in clause 5 of our <a data-udi="umb://document/b703ff07ccec43baad41fffcfcc61821" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b703ff07ccec43baad41fffcfcc61821}" title="Terms &amp; Conditions">terms and conditions</a>.</em></p>]]></locationDescription>
